Content: [dscrd-hush] <dukeleto> even these tiny bits of Hush, they can help you send many private memos in the future. I consider Hush a store-of-privacy. Each 1 HUSH is able to send 10,000 short private memos, and if you want to send larger amounts of data or store larger things, that costs more HUSH. That is the real case for "Why should I buy/hold/mine Hush?". If you think privacy is going away in society, and that it will be worth more, to YOU or others in the future, it's probably a good idea to have a bit of HUSH. And ARRR and a few other coins, too
